reviewText: No problems. Everything went well this transaction.
Thoroughly enjoy the sereies. There were some minor manufacturing glitches a few of the discs. Noting that, I highly recommend the acquisition.
Such a nice series.  Enjoying watching it again!
Several issues with product being defective and missing one season. Seller is great with communication and resolution.
Love Northern Exposure.  Sorry it was over too soon.
Season 3 discs were manufactured differently & won't work. Can't finish series :(

The cast of Northern Exposure consensus is that the town, Cicely, was the star of the show. The pulse of that town was DJ Chris Steven's music. Most of the original playlists of the classic series are gone (too much money for royalties). Musak and poor choices of obscure songs played by equally non descriptor artists are substituted.
  I hope this collection is done again with due respect to the artistic construct of this masterpiece. Until then, this is just the Mona Lisa, without her mysterious smile.
I liked this series even better watching it again.
Love the series. There have been a couple DVD's that have skipped. Not clear through the series yet so hoping there aren't anymore of lesser quality.
Outstanding!  The entire family has been sharing the videos.  Just wish there were more seasons.
Good quality. The complete set is great to have.
Forgot just how good the series really was!  I am very happy with the purchase.
